 1- ạllh ʿndh kẖṭh kbyrh kbyrh ktyr
 lkl wạḥd hly̱ hạldnyh zgẖyr kbyr
 bylwn hạlʿmr bfrḥh wḥzn yṭyr
 fyhạ sʿạdh wạ̹nt fyhạ ḥbyby tṣyr
 ạlqrạr- yạ ḥbyby yạ ạ̉ḥly̱ hdyh mn rby
 m ạ̉nt nṣyby rḥ kẖbyk jwẗ bqlby
 2- yswʿ ạlgẖạly ʿlmny ḥbk mn qlby
 wạkẖlṣlk ʿmry wạyạmy ḥty̱ ạlṣʿbh
 wạfdyk brwḥy wdmy wạqdm ḥby
 ybqy̱ ạlsr ạlly byjmʿnạ ạsmh mḥbh</lyrics>
